				<segment state="initial">
					<source>**Prepare for app updates:  **If your app will be updated, create and register a <pc dataRefEnd="id2" dataRefStart="id1" id="p1">ServicingComplete</pc> background task (see <pc dataRefEnd="id4" dataRefStart="id3" id="p2"><pc dataRefEnd="id6" dataRefStart="id5" id="p3">SystemTriggerType</pc></pc>) to help perform app updates that may be necessary outside the context of running in the foreground.</source>
